Hi Steffan,
B code means AUG67 to JULY70.  It is time to have it bored for it's first cut.
 
<< 2.) Can you use the 1600cc cylinder bores in a 1500 case without 
machining? >>

You can use 1300, 1500, 1600 and slip in 1641cc P&Cs without boring the 
cylinder holes in the case bigger.   Eric&Barb
